				<h2 class="posttitle" id="post-739"><a href="http://www.matrixmasters.net/salon/?p=739" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent link to Podcast 369 &#8211; &#8220;Timothy &#038; Terence&#8221;">Podcast 369 &#8211; &#8220;Timothy &#038; Terence&#8221;</a></h2>
			
				<div class="postentry">
				
				<p><font size="-1" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#ff0000"><strong>Guest speaker:</strong></font> <strong><font color="#0000ff">Timothy Leary &#038; Terence McKena</font><br />
<span style="color: #0000ff;">Listen</span></strong></p>
<p class="audioplayer_container"><span style="display:block;padding:5px;border:1px solid #dddddd;background:#f8f8f8" id="audioplayer_1">Audio clip: Adobe Flash Player (version 9 or above) is required to play this audio clip. Download the latest version <a href="http://www.adobe.com/shockwave/download/download.cgi?P1_Prod_Version=ShockwaveFlash&amp;promoid=BIOW" title="Download Adobe Flash Player">here</a>. You also need to have JavaScript enabled in your browser.</span></p>
<p><script type="text/javascript">AudioPlayer.embed("audioplayer_1", {soundFile:"http%3A%2F%2Fmatrixmasters.net%2Farchive%2FTerenceMcKenna%2F369-LearyMcKenna1991.mp3"});</script></p>
<p><i><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b><font color="#FF0000">Download</font><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b><font color="#FF0000"><i><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b><font color="#FF0000">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Subscribe</font></b></font></i></font></b></font></b></font></i><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b><font color="#FF0000"><br />
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><font color="#0000FF"><a href="http://matrixmasters.net/archive/TerenceMcKenna/369-LearyMcKenna1991.mp3">MP3</a></font><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b><font color="#FF0000"><i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</i><a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/matrixmasters/iGAG">Free</a></font></b></font></b></font><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b><br />
