<h3>
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/dp/0942344103/ref=nosim?tag=matrixmasterscom&#038;linkCode=sb1&#038;camp=212353&#038;creative=380549	" target="_blank">One Foot in the Future</a><br />
Nina Graboi</p>
<p><a href="http://astore.amazon.com/matrixmasterscom/detail/0226950077">Giordano Bruno and the Hermetic Tradition</a><br />
By Frances A. Yates</p>
<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Spiritual-Demonic-Magic-Campanella-History/dp/0271020458/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&#038;ie=UTF8&#038;qid=1379391558&#038;sr=1-1&#038;keywords=demonic+and+spiritual+magic">Spiritual and Demonic Magic: From Ficino to Campanella</a> (Magic in History)<br />
D.P. Walker</p>
