				<h2 class="posttitle" id="post-723"><a href="http://www.matrixmasters.net/salon/?p=723" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent link to Podcast 362 &#8211; &#8220;Flashbacks&#8221;">Podcast 362 &#8211; &#8220;Flashbacks&#8221;</a></h2>
			
				<div class="postentry">
				
				<p><font size="-1" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#ff0000"><strong>Guest speaker:</strong></font> <strong><font color="#0000ff">Timothy Leary</font><br />
